00:02:25.343 --> 00:02:41.942
What the devil meant for evil, God's going to turn around for good, and no weapon formed against you or your family will prosper.

00:02:42.756 --> 00:02:46.571
You will always be in the right place at the right time.

00:02:54.320 --> 00:03:08.948
You need to be in the spirit of the Lord more now than ever, listening to Him on a daily basis so that you are stirring yourself up.

00:03:08.948 --> 00:03:32.330
Use this video if you want to pray in the spirit; pray with me and Sister Lynn and know that God has a plan for these last days.

00:03:32.330 --> 00:03:43.789
It's not for the devil to steamroll us and take over; we have dominion and authority.

00:03:52.125 --> 00:03:54.333
We're still here until the Bride of Christ is raptured; the tribulation cannot start.

00:03:54.333 --> 00:04:01.619
I'm telling you there are great days ahead.

00:04:01.619 --> 00:04:08.372
Yes, there is great darkness, but the light is coming too.

00:04:10.173 --> 00:04:22.930
It will be like a coin that has two sides; you have the darkness and the light.

00:04:25.850 --> 00:04:29.280
You can focus on the light or the darkness.

00:04:29.280 --> 00:04:38.208
That's where we are in the end times, and I want to encourage you to pray like you've never prayed before.

00:04:38.208 --> 00:04:55.093
It's time to stand on your authority, being seated with Him in the heavenlies, far above all principalities, powers, and might.

00:05:10.474 --> 00:05:22.025
You need to know your authority and understand who you are in Christ so that you don't have a devil ramrodding you or beating you down every day with sickness, poverty, and lack.

00:05:22.025 --> 00:05:26.745
All that is under the curse.

00:05:26.745 --> 00:05:49.036
Jesus Christ came that you might have life and have it more abundantly, in abundance to the full until it overflows.

00:05:53.039 --> 00:05:58.811
